{
  "stem": "12289.2",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well then, of course, I rushed back to the embassy.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we were evacuating from there, because you never knew.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You never knew if the-- what the Germans were going to-- to do if-- if they knew that we were hiding him.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we took him away from there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we were hiding him then on different places in the-- in the city.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And to make a long story short, just-- he was living with me, towards the end.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We'll just say in-- in January, beginning of January, 1945, in-- I had a small-- small room I had up in the-- near the-- the palace, up in the middle of-- of Buda.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no, no.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We-- I had to move from there, already.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And so I was hiding him in there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then-- and then I told his son-in-law, which was-- became a very good friend of mine, Gyorgy Libik, who was in the resistance.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he-- I told-- I said to him, now, you take my car now.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And you go over to Pest side, because I had the feeling that the Soviets will come very soon.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And that he did.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And after he had went over, with his father-in-law, the Germans blew up all the bridges.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "The-- the Soviets came into the Pest side, attacked the Pest side and all that.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And he came into contact with the Soviets, this Professor Szent-Gyorgy.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And they brought him to Moscow, where he was-- they paid tribute to him there as the big man.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And-- and that then he was going to be the head of state and all that and so on.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
